            "id": 6195691,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 深證成指下跌-392.2點至12694.2049點，跌幅3%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間17日02:36，深證成指下跌392.2點（或3%），暫報12694.20點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-4.66%</li><li>近 1 月：+0.17%</li><li>近 3 月：+22.07%</li><li>近 6 月：+33.88%</li><li>今年以來：+29.72%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>培育鑽石概念領跌-4.81%。其中    四方達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300179:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300179\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300179-CN</a>)            下跌        8.47%            ;        楚江新材(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002171:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002171\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002171-CN</a>)            下跌        7.86%            ;        晶盛機電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300316:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300316\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300316-CN</a>)            下跌        6.71%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>虛擬電廠概念領跌-4.38%。其中    中恆電氣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002364:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002364\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002364-CN</a>)            下跌        9.99%            ;        科陸電子(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002121:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002121\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002121-CN</a>)            下跌        9.97%            ;        中電鑫龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002298:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002298\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002298-CN</a>)            下跌        9.93%    。</p></section></main>",
